  "text": "containing a variety of plasticizers, colorants, flame retardants, and fillers, in addition to a fraction of metals and ceramics [CITATION_1] . One way to utilize this material is as a reducing agent in metallurgical processes. Plastics are composed of long polymeric chains of carbon and hydrogen; for this reason, they are potential candidates to substitute the traditionally used reducing agents [CITATION_2] . Utilizing residue materials in general and, specifically SRM in metallurgical processes not only reduces the dependency on the fossil coal, but can also lead to a more sustainable way to manage these materials [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
